data.description: Rental Property for sale with a lease already in place! Great investment opportunity! Immaculate 2-story 4-bedroom 2.5 bath townhome with a Game Room in beautiful Village Grove. No back neighbors! Custom-built kitchen includes customized wood cabinets, pantry door, marble floors, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances including a separate stainless steel ice maker, dual fuel range, reverse osmosis filtration system, upgraded lighting with granite counters, and a kitchen island! Formal dining, laminate wood flooring, neutral paint colors, and a stunning two-story high-ceiling family room!  French doors off the primary bedroom lead out to the fenced-in patio. Game room upstairs with 3 additional bedrooms! Iron patio gate plus much more.
